Title: The Fruits of Our Labor
Description:
You put on quite the show, yes? The orders are already coming in. The citizens can't wait to get their mandibles on the potions.

I have one final task for you. I want you to take these latest orders and deliver them. You will accept, yes? 

The citizens are stirring. Now is the time to show the Pale Weavelashers what we can do. If any try and stop you, you know what to do.
ObjectivesText: Deliver 3 Brightshade Potions to Silken Ward citizens.
CompletionText: The time is now, friend. The Pale Weavelashers aren't unstoppable.
RewardText: Well done, friend. The citizens have all they need to overcome the Pale Weavelashers.
